                <reference>M. A. Bobodzhanova. Justification of the Regularization Method for Nonlinear Integro-Differential Equations with Zero Operator of the Differential Part // MPEI Bulletin. - 2011. - № 6. - Pp. 85-95. (In Russian)</reference>
                <reference>M. A. Bobodzhanova. Laurent Series for Solutions of Fredholm Integro-Differential Equations with Zero Operator of the Differential Part //MPEI Bulletin. -2015. - No. 3. - Pp. 134-138. (In Russian)</reference>
