                <reference>V. I. Kachalov, D. A. Maslov. On analytical solutions of nonlinear perturbation theory problems. Siberian Electronic Mathematical News. 2025, 22:1, pp. 457-464. (In Russian)</reference>
                <reference>V. I. Kachalov. Pseudoanalytic solutions of singularly perturbed equations in Banach algebras. Dokl. RAS. Matem., Inform., Proc. exercise. - 2025. - 525:5. - P. 57-61. (In Russian)</reference>
